M|references|Provide affiliates with:
M|references|- [ ] Unique tracking links/codes
M|references|- [ ] Product overview and key benefits
M|references|- [ ] Target audience description
M|references|- [ ] Comparison to cp
M|references|- [ ] Creative assets (logos, banners, images)
M|references|- [ ] Sample copy and talking points
M|references|- [ ] Case studies and testimonials
M|references|- [ ] Demo access or free account
M|references|- [ ] FAQ and objection handling
M|references|- [ ] Payment terms and schedule
